    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College fee is affordable. Even the college provide activities for over all personality development of students.",
          "name": "Supriya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Courses are well desinged and provide knowledge",
          "name": "MEGHA MITRA",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The coordination received from the teachers and the college staff",
          "name": "Laxmi Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College is safe from ragging, I didn't face any kind of ragging.",
          "name": "Shalil Kumar Rai",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The facilities of classroom, library and canteen.",
          "name": "Ruchi Dey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Activities in the college and events I made nre new who were good",
          "name": "Shrest Jaiswal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The classrooms are digitalized and air conditioned. They maintain good cleanliness and hygiene. The best part is the infrastructure.",
          "name": "Aryan Jaiswal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Library is really beautiful and eyecatching",
          "name": "Shagufta Farheen",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the sports arena a lot where we can spent time with our friends.",
          "name": "Yunus ali",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the library a lot there i can spend a lot of time reading all the books because there is a lot of varieties of books out there .",
          "name": "Yunus ali",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Lack of hostel facilities for boys. Only reliable on pgs and rented rooms in the area.",
          "name": "Ap Swastik",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college should have a parking facility for the students",
          "name": "Laxmi Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Though the college has students lift but sometimes we have to wait in the queue so i think they shoud increase the numbers.",
          "name": "Laxmi Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the other courses are not that good except b.com and BBA",
          "name": "MEGHA MITRA",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sometime the there are too many activities going on in collage at the same time so one can’t participate in all at the same time",
          "name": "Rishit Jaiswal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sometimes the college takes a lot of time to reply to the mails.",
          "name": "Parth agarwal",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The behaviour of some of the seniors is also very problematic",
          "name": "Manav Mantry",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The events are usually capped to around 200 to 300 students so many times we aren't able to join the events.",
          "name": "Rishabh Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "No college life because no one attends college and csmpus is very small this making it a very crowded place",
          "name": "Harsh Dugar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Minimal activities in clubs and societies.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
